## 4 Simulation examples

A mass–spring–damper system is used to verify the proposed approach [34]. The system dynamics:
$$
m\ddot x + F_f + F_s = u(t).
$$

(Parameters, fuzzy-controller gains, and initial state used in simulation are listed in the original manuscript; see Figures 5–8 and Tables 1–5 for numerical results and plots.)

